WEBVTT

00:06:59.400 --> 00:07:02.536
There ends up being this idea,
oh, introverts are antisocial,

00:07:02.560 --> 00:07:05.936
and I always say, it's not that,
it's just differently social.

00:07:05.960 --> 00:07:07.416
AG: When you meet someone new,

00:07:07.440 --> 00:07:11.176
introversion-extraversion
is often the very first thing you notice.

00:07:11.200 --> 00:07:13.336
You can even pick up clues
in a split second,

00:07:13.360 --> 00:07:14.680
before they've said a word.

00:07:16.840 --> 00:07:18.816
Hey Allison?
Allison: Yeah?

00:07:18.840 --> 00:07:20.096
AG: Allison is my wife.

00:07:20.120 --> 00:07:21.496
What are you doing?

00:07:21.520 --> 00:07:22.736
A: Googling you.

00:07:22.760 --> 00:07:24.016
AG: What did you find?

00:07:24.040 --> 00:07:27.374
A: Just you in the middle of a speech,
or with your mouth hanging open.

00:07:27.398 --> 00:07:28.405
AG: (Laughs)

00:07:28.429 --> 00:07:30.056
AG: It's always interesting to see